  <header class="article-header">
    <h1>Robert De Niro Doesn't Give a F*ck About Your Stupid Startup</h1>
    <div class="by-line">
      <a title="Sophie  Kleeman's Profile" class="link-author avatar avatar-small" href="../../profiles/152573/sophie-kleeman">
        <img alt="Sophie  Kleeman's avatar image" class="no-share-btns" src="http://media3.mic.com/ZjIxZDc0OThlNCMvUHEyeWVCaHBmN1plYnNsZzJkWTM5dG54cnlrPS8yNXgyNS9zbWFydC9odHRwczovL3MzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20vcG9saWN5bWljLWltYWdlcy84ZmJlOWVkNWU1YTFlNzc5YTdmOTA0YTU5NDNhOWVmN2QyMjY2ODA3YjEwZTgxNDUyM2I0MTY3NDc1ODY0ZGNjLmpwZw==.jpg">
      </a>
      By
      <a title="Sophie  Kleeman's Profile" class="link-author name" href="../../profiles/152573/sophie-kleeman">Sophie  Kleeman</a>
      <time datetime="2015-11-06T20:05:06.000Z" pubdate="">November 06, 2015</time>
    </div>
    <div class="share-facebook-twitter subhead">
      <span class="fb-like-container-text">Like Mic on Facebook:</span>
      <span class="fb-button">
        <div class="fb-like-top fb-like" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/thefutureisnowbymic" data-width="300" data-keen-tracking-name="subhed" data-keen-social-channel="facebook_future" data-show-faces="false" data-send="false" data-layout="button"></div>
      </span>
    </div>
  </header>
  <div id="article-body" class="article-body share-media-toolbar-block"><div class="share-media share-media-side-fold">
  <ul><li class="share-media-facebook"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128091%2Frobert-de-niro-to-slack-founder-i-dont-give-a-fck-who-you-are" title="Share on Facebook" rel:gt_act="share/facebook/share" rel:gt_label="true" name="fb_share" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-facebook modal-trigger-facebook k-trackable-share" data-fb-link="http://mic.com/articles/128091/robert-de-niro-to-slack-founder-i-dont-give-a-fck-who-you-are" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="facebook" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307534536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-facebook"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>SHARE</a></div></li>
<li class="share-media-twitter"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128091%2Frobert-de-niro-to-slack-founder-i-dont-give-a-fck-who-you-are&amp;original_referer=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128091%2Frobert-de-niro-to-slack-founder-i-dont-give-a-fck-who-you-are&amp;related=MicNews&amp;source=tweetbutton&amp;text=Robert%20De%20Niro%20Doesn't%20Give%20a%20F*ck%20About%20Your%20Stupid%20Startup%20by%20%40sophie_kleeman&amp;via=MicNews" title="Share on Twitter" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-twitter k-trackable-share" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="twitter" data-popup-height="380" data-popup-width="660" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307534536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-twitter"></i><i class="social-icon-divider"></i>TWEET</a></div></li>
<li class="share-media-tumblr"><div class="share-button-count"><a href="http://tumblr.com/share/link?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmic.com%2Farticles%2F128091%2Frobert-de-niro-to-slack-founder-i-dont-give-a-fck-who-you-are&amp;description=Shots%20fired.&amp;name=Robert%20De%20Niro%20Doesn't%20Give%20a%20F*ck%20About%20Your%20Stupid%20Startup" title="Share on Tumblr" target="_new" class="share-button share-button-medium-tumblr k-trackable-share" data-keen-tracking-name="sidefold-share" data-keen-social-channel="tumblr" data-popup-width="450" data-popup-height="483" data-facebook-pixel-id="6028307534536"><i class="social-icon-mini social-icon-mini-tumblr"></i><i-social-icon-divider></i-social-icon-divider>POST</a></div></li></ul>
  <div class="corner"></div>
</div>
<div class="article-body-content"><p class="">You <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lQkpes3dgzg">talkin' to</a> Slack? Robert De Niro is, and he is not into it.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="">On Wednesday, t<span class="comment-selection" data-editor-comment-id="8064d895-7d28-42b4-9b93-ade5f1dee8a4">he </span><i><span class="comment-selection" data-editor-comment-id="8064d895-7d28-42b4-9b93-ade5f1dee8a4">Taxi Driver </span></i><span class="comment-selection" data-editor-comment-id="8064d895-7d28-42b4-9b93-ade5f1dee8a4">and <i>New Year's Eve</i>&nbsp;actor attended WSJ. Magazine Innovator Awards t</span>o present Angelina Jolie with an award in the entertainment and film category.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="">Prior to De Niro's appearance, Steven Butterfield, co-founder of the messaging app <a href="https://slack.com/">Slack</a>, went onstage to accept an award and attempted a few jokes, noting that he felt a tad out of place.&nbsp;</p>
<p class="">"We are a long way from San Francisco," he said upon receiving what he termed a "nerd award," according to <a href="http://pagesix.com/2015/11/05/robert-de-niro-drops-f-bomb-on-condescending-tech-mogul/" style="font-style: italic;">Page Six</a>.<i> </i>Then he set his sights on De Niro. "I watched <i>Godfather II</i> on the plane ... when you killed Don Fanucci, I liked that."</p>
<p class="">Maybe De Niro was having a bad day. Maybe he's a <a href="https://www.hipchat.com/">HipChat</a> fan. Maybe he felt threatened by Butterfield, who looks like a&nbsp;<a href="http://blogs-images.forbes.com/miguelhelft/files/2015/02/Slack-e1423705727366-1940x1089.jpg" class="hoverZoomLink">younger, richer version</a>&nbsp;of De Niro. Maybe De Niro wishes he were the co-founder of a <a href="http://bits.blogs.nytimes.com/2015/04/16/is-slack-really-worth-2-8-billion-a-conversation-with-stewart-butterfield/?_r=0">$2.8 billion</a> company. Whatever it was, the actor wasn't having it, and launched a shady tirade at the tech executive.</p>
<p class="">"Whoever the last speaker was," De Niro began,&nbsp;<a href="http://pagesix.com/2015/11/05/robert-de-niro-drops-f-bomb-on-condescending-tech-mogul/">according to</a>&nbsp;<i>Page Six</i>.&nbsp;"I thought you were a bit condescending to us actors ... celebrities. I'm gonna go on record with you just to say that. And I don't give a fuck who you are." &nbsp;</p>
<figure contenteditable="false" class="embeddable clearfix image article-image-container article-image-container-horizontal photo embeddable-image" id="embeddable-qjqsa18" data-type="image"><div class="embeddable-container"><img src="http://thumbs.mic.com/ZDMwMDIxM2FjMiMvNFFhcGx3RHhjN1BVWC1BazJLVDdsV2NxdFRrPS83eDE0MDozMDg5eDE5NTYvOTAweDUzMC9maWx0ZXJzOnF1YWxpdHkoNzApL2h0dHA6Ly9zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tL3BvbGljeW1pYy1pbWFnZXMvNGR3MjRkM3RnZGJ3emI3YTNwa2l3ZnFiYzM0c3NwN2Jyb2JkOG1waGh1ZDFlc2hnb3l5Nmd6aGs3andpbWV6OS5qcGc=.jpg" alt="Robert De Niro Doesn't Give a F*ck About Your Stupid Startup"></div><figcaption class="article-embeddable-caption">Stewart Butterfield speaking at the 2015 WSJ. Magazine Innovator Awards</figcaption><figcaption class="article-embeddable-attribution">Source:&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gettyimages.com/" class="article-embeddable-source">Kevin Mazur/Getty Images</a></figcaption></figure>
<p class="">Ah, yes. Isn't it great when a member of one self-congratulatory profession finds fault in a member of another self-congratulatory profession?</p>
<p class="">Luckily (or unluckily, depending on your penchant for ridiculous rich-people catfights), Butterfield took the barb in stride, tweeting the following photo that night: &nbsp;</p>
<figure contenteditable="false" data-url="https://twitter.com/stewart/status/662104355194150912?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" class="embeddable clearfix embeddable-twitter embeddable-twit-pic" data-twitterhtml="<blockquote lang=&quot;en&quot; class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;><p>I just literally got trash-talked by Robert De Niro. &amp;quot;I don't know who the FUCK you are.&amp;quot; #lifegoals pic.twitter.com/j9yT5ZiU4A</p><a href=&quot;https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTBEZkWWoAAUoxZ.jpg:large&quot;>https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTBEZkWWoAAUoxZ.jpg:large</a><a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/stewart/status/662104355194150912?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&quot;></a><script async=&quot;async&quot; src=&quot;//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js&quot; charset=&quot;utf-8&quot;></script></blockquote>" id="embeddable-tjtpcho" data-type="twitter"><div class="embeddable-container"><blockquote lang="en" class="twitter-tweet"><p>I just literally got trash-talked by Robert De Niro. "I don't know who the FUCK you are." #lifegoals pic.twitter.com/j9yT5ZiU4A</p><a href="https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTBEZkWWoAAUoxZ.jpg:large">https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CTBEZkWWoAAUoxZ.jpg:large</a><a href="https://twitter.com/stewart/status/662104355194150912?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw"></a><script async="async" src="http://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></blockquote></div></figure>
